				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div style="display:none; right:10px;" class="metadata topicon nopopups" id="good-star"><a href="Wikipedia_Good_articles" title="This is a good article. Click here for more information."><img alt="This is a good article. Click here for more information." src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Symbol_support_vote.svg/15px-Symbol_support_vote.svg.png" width="15" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Symbol_support_vote.svg/23px-Symbol_support_vote.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/94/Symbol_support_vote.svg/30px-Symbol_support_vote.svg.png 2x" /></a></div>
<table class="infobox vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold; font-style: italic">A Community of Witches: Contemporary Neo-Paganism and Witchcraft in the United States</th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:A_Community_of_Witches.jpg" class="image"><img alt="A Community of Witches.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/A_Community_of_Witches.jpg/200px-A_Community_of_Witches.jpg" width="200" height="308" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/A_Community_of_Witches.jpg/300px-A_Community_of_Witches.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e7/A_Community_of_Witches.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
